was the fadeaway.

00:01:16.500 --> 00:01:17.500
Right?

00:01:17.500 --> 00:01:18.500
Broadway: Signature.

00:01:18.500 --> 00:01:20.400
Speaker 1: Now, Broadway right here, he's
going to show us how that fadeaway works.

00:01:20.400 --> 00:01:21.400
Very, very effective move . . .

