Broadway: Turn and then the shot.

00:01:45.710 --> 00:01:46.710
Speaker 1: Oh.

00:01:46.710 --> 00:01:47.710
Like that.

00:01:47.710 --> 00:01:48.710
Broadway: Mike gets such great elevation.

00:01:48.710 --> 00:01:49.710
Speaker 1: Right.

00:01:49.710 --> 00:01:50.710
Broadway: Hard to defend the shot.

00:01:50.710 --> 00:01:51.710
Speaker 1: Yes.

00:01:51.710 --> 00:01:52.710
Broadway: But, this is what it looks like.

00:01:52.710 --> 00:01:53.710
Speaker 1: Nice.

